Class Pawn

chess.Piece

All Implemented Interfaces:
ChessPiece
public class Pawn extends Piece
Pawn piece
  • can move 2 on first move
  • after must move 1
  • captures diagonally

En Passent - if the pawn on the first x2 would have been caputured in a 1x move, they are captured as if they made a 1x move
